overview: In this newest video from Odyssey there are full length parts from team riders: Matt Beringer; Adam Banton; Aaron Ross; Gary Young; Mike Aitken; Taj Mihelich; Chase Hawk; Jim Cielencki, & Jimmy Levan. In this 2-Disc DVD set, the second disc features both of the previous Odyssey videos plus tons of bonus material. New video run time is about 60 minutes.
title: Odyssey - Electronical
